/[Tt]emp/
/[Oo]bj/
/[Bb]uild/
/[Bb]uilds/
/Assets/AssetStoreTools/
/Assets/StreamingAssets/

# Autogenerated VS/MD/Rider solution and project files
/[Ee]xternal/[Pp]rojects/
[Aa]ssembly-[Cc][Ss]harp.csproj
[Aa]ssembly-[Cc][Ss]harp-[Ee]ditor.csproj
